{"tid":1167761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【網絡衛生】各位時事台巴絲，若要引用親中媒體，請記得先archive，唔好貼原link","createTime":"2019-05-23T09:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T12:18:31.000Z","uid":131691,"like":132,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad647ae3b001925537a84c72b691e5b5547c72b","tid":1167761,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:06:31.000Z","msg":"排除部份真心三毛或假膠，每逢張貼親中媒體嘅嘢，請先用archive過濾，因爲：<br />\n1. 網絡有referrer header，你直接喺連登link會畀佢哋見到有人由連登過去（亦即確認連登三毛政治宣傳效率嘅其中一個指標）<br />\n2. 會員嘅IP直入親中媒體嘅server log（個人網絡衛生，尤其 .cn 嗰啲網隨時有Javascript malware）<br />\n3. 如果係Youtube等社交媒體化嘅平台，你貼原link變相幫佢推上香港熱門（變相幫手政治宣傳）<br />\n4. 防止親中撚炒車後del原post，e.g. 《幫講出聲》Facebook page造假新聞話反送中遊行有人畀錢請人參加，但係其實係自己WhatsApp綠色post<br />\n<br />\n至於點archive，有以下選擇，好簡單咁copy and paste個網頁URL就得：<br />\n1. 文字或圖文並茂但靜態嘅網站，如新聞或社論等： <a href=\"https://archive.today/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.today%2F&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyow2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=14aa88e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.today/</a><br />\n2. Youtube 或其它影片： <a href=\"https://streamable.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyow2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=e835e055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/</a><br />\n3. 動態網站，如Facebook, Twitter, Instagram： 最好screenshot，當然記得crop走個人名+相，如果唔係變相自爆"},{"pid":"6dc9392ebdc1508949e25af3f0b67d43c276eb52","tid":1167761,"uid":131691,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:09:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://archive.today\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.today&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyow2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=a12a5c29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.today</a> 其實可以用嚟archive Facebook post，但係你要有個post URL先得（share畀自己Messenger會有條link）"},{"pid":"9875fab7e576b1b0f61f64bdbc2b02a27c246845","tid":1167761,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20